OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1777129865
OL,3,CMore than 35,000 Southampton fans head
OL,4,Cto Wembley for FA Cup semi-final
OL,6,FThousands of Southampton fans are
OL,7,Fheading to Wembley as Saints take on
OL,8,FManchester City in the FA Cup semi-
OL,9,Ffinal.
OL,11,FSouthampton have been given permission
OL,12,Fto once again wear their commemorative
OL,13,Fyellow shirt ` which celebrates their
OL,14,Fsole FA Cup triumph against Manchester
OL,15,FUnited as a Second Division outfit in
OL,16,F1976 ` as they take inspiration from
OL,17,FLawrie McMenemy's victorious team.
OL,19,FA convoy of 54 coaches will be leaving
OL,20,FSt Mary's on Saturday morning.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
