PN,41202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1777129865
OL,3,CMore than 35,000 Southampton fans head
OL,4,Cto Wembley for FA Cup semi-final
OL,6,FFans are being warned not to travel by
OL,7,Ftrain and consider alternative travel
OL,8,Fdue to major engineering works.
OL,10,FSouth Western Railway says the work,
OL,11,Fwhich has been planned since 2024,
OL,12,Fmust be completed before the summer to
OL,13,Favoid speed restrictions and reduced
OL,14,Fperformance at one of the busiest
OL,15,Fparts of the SWR network.
OL,17,FThe train operator said though
OL,18,Fadditional services will run, it won't
OL,19,Fbe enough to cater for all the fans
OL,20,Fhoping to travel on the railway.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
