OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1777129865
OL,3,CMore than 35,000 Southampton fans head
OL,4,Cto Wembley for FA Cup semi-final
OL,6,FFor those that are heading to
OL,7,FSouthampton Central, supporters will
OL,8,Fjoin a queuing system to board the
OL,9,Fnext available train.
OL,11,FOther stations including Fareham,
OL,12,FHavant, Clapham Junction and London
OL,13,FWaterloo are expected to be busier
OL,14,Fthan usual.
OL,16,FFans hoping to travel out of the city
OL,17,Fusing Northam Bridge were faced with
OL,18,Flong delays earlier this morning after
OL,19,Fa serious crash forced the closure of
OL,20,Fthe bridge.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1777129865
OL,3,CMore than 35,000 Southampton fans head
OL,4,Cto Wembley for FA Cup semi-final
OL,6,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,7,Fscene between Kent Street and
OL,8,FAthelstan Road, and the bridge was
OL,9,Fshut in both directions while crews
OL,10,Frespond to the incident.
OL,12,FThe bridge was reopened just after 9am.
OL,14,FFans will be hoping that Saints can
OL,15,Fperform a repeat of their 1976 FA Cup
OL,16,Fwin.
OL,18,FGlen de la Cour from Total Saints
OL,19,FPodcast was just seven when Saints won
OL,20,Fthe FA cup back in 1976.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
