PN,41205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1777129865
OL,3,CMore than 35,000 Southampton fans head
OL,4,Cto Wembley for FA Cup semi-final
OL,6,FHe believes they can do it again.
OL,7,FSpeaking to ITV Meridian about that
OL,8,Fhistoric moment he said: "I couldn't
OL,9,Fgo to Wembley because dad couldn't get
OL,10,Ftickets.
OL,12,F"I remember watching the game in our
OL,13,Ffront room in Netley on the little
OL,14,Ftelly we had there.
OL,16,F"I remember when Bobby Stokes scored
OL,17,Fand my dad was doing laps of the front
OL,18,Froom.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1777129865
OL,3,CMore than 35,000 Southampton fans head
OL,4,Cto Wembley for FA Cup semi-final
OL,6,F"Magic from 1976 would certainly help,
OL,7,Fbut obviously more importantly, the
OL,8,Fmanager's got to get the game-playing
OL,9,Fright and the players have got to play
OL,10,Fit out and bring the energy."
OL,12,FThe last time Southampton made an FA
OL,13,FCup final was 2003, but the team lost
OL,14,F1-0 to Arsenal.
OL,16,FManager at the time Gordon Strachan
OL,17,Fsays with Saints on a 20 match
OL,18,Funbeaten run maybe they can spring a
OL,19,Fsurprise.
OL,21,F"It's getting to the final," he said.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1777129865
OL,3,CMore than 35,000 Southampton fans head
OL,4,Cto Wembley for FA Cup semi-final
OL,6,F"I've got to say - the run that
OL,7,Fthey're on just now has been
OL,8,Fabsolutely phenomenal.
OL,10,F"Unfortunately they are going up
OL,11,Fagainst one of the best teams in
OL,12,FEurope."
OL,14,FKick-off at Wembley is at 5:15pm.
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/7
